data.description: Wow, Wow, Wow.....Look at what is Brand New in this home this year: ROOF, HVAC, FLOORING, PAINT, LIGTHING, BACK DECK. Tons of space in this well keep home in the Grayson Valley Golf Community area. Huge Great with abundant natural lighting, spacious rooms and huge open back deck open to a huge fence in flat back yard. The basement is full of play space office, bedroom, and office...including a 2 car garage.
